<item>
            <title>[LU-8826] recovery hard time should not be shrunk for IR</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8826</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Otherwise, soft limit will be very close to hard limit, and on sluggish network, extended soft limit can reach hard limit easily, and the whole recovery will be aborted easier. Actually, IR is used to shorten the client reconnect time during recovery, so shrink soft limit is good enough. It doesn&apos;t make sense to shrink the hard limit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
